The retail of the Volkswagen Polo 1.0 TSI 85kW DSG derivatives will commence from late February 2022. The Polo 1.0 TSI 85kW DSG derivatives will join the Polo 1.0 TSI 70kW Manual and Polo GTI derivatives which went on sale at the beginning of January 2022. Volkswagen sold 1,455 units of the new Polo in the first month of retail. The 1.0 TSI 85kW DSG derivatives account for 40% of the sales volume of the Polo model range. The Polo Life 1.0 TSI 85kW DSG comes standard with a digital dashboard display, Park Distance Control (front and rear), electric folding mirrors, lumbar support for the driver and front passenger, a leather-wrapped multi-function steering wheel with shift paddles as well as 15-inch Essex alloy wheels. The Polo R-Line 1.0 TSI 85kW DSG distinguishes itself from the other Polo versions by its striking ‘R’ design. In addition to the standard features of the Polo Life, the Polo R-Line is offered with 16-inch Valencia alloy wheels, Composition Media infotainment system with inductive mobile charging and a two-zone climatronic air-conditioning system.  <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-558016" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/VWPolo-2022.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="665" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/VWPolo-2022.jpg 1000w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/VWPolo-2022-300x200.jpg 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/VWPolo-2022-768x511.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-558020" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/VW-Polo-GT-2022.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="665" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/VW-Polo-GT-2022.jpg 1000w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/VW-Polo-GT-2022-300x200.jpg 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-cont